Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.35,0:00:08.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Lucas!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.75,0:00:11.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah Anda selamat.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.31,0:00:13.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Party kita...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.91,0:00:16.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,telah musnah.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.61,0:01:54.91,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Pasti terjadi sesuatu padanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.91,0:01:56.98,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Dia bersama Jasmine.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.98,0:01:58.31,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Dia pasti baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.31,0:01:59.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,firasatku tidak enak.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.98,0:02:04.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti,\Nakan kulaporkan ke pihak Guild.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.45,0:02:06.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.41,0:02:09.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.75,0:02:10.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.95,0:02:13.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.27,0:02:14.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah sadar.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Elijah,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.35,0:02:19.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,ambil mutiara di sarung tanganku...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.31,0:02:40.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.11,0:02:46.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa Jasmine baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.55,0:02:48.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia ada di sebelah sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.91,0:02:51.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia terkena serangan Lucas.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.75,0:02:54.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuhnya sedang tak dilindungi Mana.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuobati seadanya,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.95,0:03:00.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi mungkin ada luka dalam.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berikan mutiara itu padanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.91,0:03:12.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Napasnya mulai membaik.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah aku bawa mutiara penyembuhan\Ndari ibuku.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana keadaanmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah sehat, buat maraton pun kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.55,0:03:27.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.51,0:03:30.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa sangka pendekar bertopeng\Nyang mengikuti tes bersamaku
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,ternyata bocah seumuranku.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Topengku tak ada!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, aku tak menemukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan tongkat pedangku?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.55,0:03:44.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah menyimpannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.35,0:03:54.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,sudah menyelamatkanku dan Jasmine.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.54,0:03:58.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal kau bisa saja kabur sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.58,0:04:05.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku mengorbankan kalian\Nyang sedang sekarat,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.85,0:04:09.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku tak ada bedanya\Ndengan si bajingan Lucas itu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.85,0:04:11.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sama sekali berbeda dengannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.45,0:04:16.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku takkan pernah memaafkan Lucas.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.31,0:04:19.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia benar-benar ingin membunuhmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.75,0:04:21.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan Jasmine juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.71,0:04:22.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.25,0:04:25.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.31,0:04:31.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, kenapa kau tak kabur\Nsaat Elder Wood muncul?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal Jasmine sudah\Nmenyuruhmu melarikan diri.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.78,0:04:38.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena raja takkan meninggalkan rakyatnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.85,0:04:44.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.21,0:04:48.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku sudah berjanji akan melindungi\Norang-orang yang berharga bagiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menjanjikan hal seperti itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.41,0:04:55.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kehidupan macam apa\Nyang kau jalani selama ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.36,0:05:00.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berapa lama aku tak sadarkan diri?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.05,0:05:03.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin lebih dari sehari.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.65,0:05:07.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita belum bisa bergerak\Nsampai Jasmine pulih.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.62,0:05:12.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namaku Arthur. Arthur Leywin.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.91,0:05:17.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau boleh panggil aku Art.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.63,0:05:22.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini tiba-tiba, tapi...\NElijah Knight dari Kerajaan Darv.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.95,0:05:26.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dilihat dari mana pun,\Nini bukan benda alami, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yang membuat tempat bernaung\Ndari besi ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.01,0:05:33.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kubuat dengan sihir saat guanya runtuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.01,0:05:34.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.73,0:05:37.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sehebat apa pun sihirmu,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,mustahil bisa menciptakan besi\Ndari ketiadaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Singkatnya, apa kau seorang dwarf?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.91,0:05:47.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya aku tak bisa\Nmenyembunyikannya lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.15,0:05:50.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soal aku dwarf atau bukan,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku sendiri pun tak tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.31,0:05:56.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dibesarkan di Kerajaan Darv,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi Tetua Rahdeas yang merawatku,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.88,0:06:01.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,selalu menghindar\Njika kutanya soal orang tuaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.01,0:06:07.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ingatan masa kecilku hanyalah\Nkepingan sedih yang tak bisa kupahami.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.81,0:06:11.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski begitu,\Naku menjalani hidup yang normal.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.56,0:06:16.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hingga Mana Core-ku mencapai\Ntahap oranye pekat,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.85,0:06:20.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku pingsan setelah diserang\Noleh gelombang energi aneh.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat aku sadar,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.11,0:06:28.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku sudah dikelilingi\Nbesi hitam yang tajam.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.41,0:06:33.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah itu, Tetua Rahdeas menyuruhku\Npergi dari Darv.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.01,0:06:37.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya sudah waktunya aku pergi\Nke tempat lain di Benua Dicathen.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanpa tahu apa alasannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.11,0:06:44.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya terjadi begitu cepat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.01,0:06:46.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ditambah, energi itu masih sering kumat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.58,0:06:48.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perasaanku waktu itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.25,0:06:53.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,kupikir mungkin ada hubungannya\Ndengan kekuatan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hidupmu juga berat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.78,0:07:03.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan makan ikan itu, Arthur!\NYang ini pasti lebih enak!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.18,0:07:10.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.41,0:07:13.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bermaksud merusak suasana.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak usah khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, bagaimana denganmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.66,0:07:20.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku sudah bercerita,\Nsekarang giliranmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.25,0:07:23.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jurus yang kau pakai\Nsaat mengalahkan Elder Wood...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.29,0:07:27.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rambutmu memutih dan muncul\Ntanda bercahaya di tubuhmu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.66,0:07:28.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.05,0:07:31.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Matamu juga berubah ungu muda.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.58,0:07:37.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ini Augmenter yang bisa\Nmengendalikan empat elemen
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan punya dua atribut tambahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Es dan petir.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.38,0:07:46.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kukira kau orang yang berbeda,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi sepertinya aku kalah darimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.88,0:07:50.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.98,0:07:52.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, apa tanda dan warna matamu\Nyang berubah itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.95,0:07:57.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ini Beast Tamer.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.45,0:08:01.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang kau lihat itu adalah\NTekad Beast milikku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tekad Beast?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu?\NBerapa umurmu sebenarnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.51,0:08:07.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dua bulan lalu, umurku genap 11 tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata aku lebih tua darimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku baru saja umur 12 tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.38,0:08:16.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi jadi lebih tua tak ada gunanya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.71,0:08:24.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa wajahmu begitu?\NSudah kuduga kau lebih aneh dariku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah kau sadar, Jasmine.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sungguh minta maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.91,0:08:50.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya baik-baik saja, Jasmine.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.91,0:08:54.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.55,0:08:57.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku gagal melindungimu lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu itu, aku bertindak keras kepala.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya aku yang minta maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.91,0:09:09.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah menyeretmu\Nke dalam situasi sulit seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuh Jasmine terasa sekecil ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lukamu... Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang aku tak apa-apa, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang lebih penting,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.65,0:09:25.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,bagaimana kita keluar dari sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.98,0:09:38.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutmu, apa ada yang selamat selain kita?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.98,0:09:40.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Reginald dan Brald
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.95,0:09:43.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,gugur sebelum kau mengalahkan Elder Wood.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.71,0:09:46.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan Samantha?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.19,0:09:51.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku membuat tempat bernaung\Nsebelum guanya runtuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.11,0:09:54.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi keadaannya kacau,\Njadi aku tak tahu dia selamat atau tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.45,0:09:58.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kita bisa mencarinya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.55,0:10:01.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana-ku sudah pulih, kurasa sekarang bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketemu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kemampuan pelacakan yang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.00,0:10:48.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa anak ini sebenarnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Samantha.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia masih hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.98,0:11:04.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan dicabut!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.45,0:11:09.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akar itu menahan pendarahan di kakinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.55,0:11:13.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Denyut jantungnya normal\Ndan napasnya juga stabil.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.95,0:11:17.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nyawanya sudah tidak terancam.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.25,0:11:23.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lukanya cukup parah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.41,0:11:31.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang akan kau lakukan\Ndengan Mana Core Elder Wood ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.45,0:11:35.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti susah mencarinya di reruntuhan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Awas runtuh!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.31,0:11:59.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial, apa ini ulah Lucas?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Percuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo bergegas!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita tak bisa lewat atas.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo cari rute lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Air bawah tanah?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.28,0:12:54.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial, jumlahnya cukup banyak untuk\Nmenghidupkan kembali Elder Wood.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada jalan keluar!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita harus menyelam.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.95,0:13:02.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jasmine, bawa Samantha!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.21,0:13:12.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nyawa yang sudah kuselamatkan,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.81,0:13:15.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,takkan kubiarkan mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.55,0:13:31.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jasmine!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.38,0:13:33.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Elijah!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tempat ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.95,0:13:41.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beast?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Banyak sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.58,0:13:49.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita dikepung.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.58,0:14:12.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Takkan ada habisnya kalau begini!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jasmine!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.31,0:14:26.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Elijah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.11,0:14:38.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi-lagi, aku
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.38,0:14:43.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,gagal melindungi\Norang-orang yang berharga bagiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.61,0:15:03.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,di dunia ini pun,\Naku akan mati dalam kesendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.71,0:15:07.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.01,0:15:24.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku datang, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.95,0:15:27.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sylvie.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.75,0:15:37.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah besar, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.91,0:15:41.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berat badanmu dan tinggimu...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jasmine! Elijah!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.51,0:15:55.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makhluk itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Naga?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.11,0:15:59.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi dia punya empat kaki.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mustahil itu naga, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu naga betulan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.18,0:16:14.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Naga?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namanya Sylvie, rekanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.01,0:16:23.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi naga diyakini sudah punah\Nratusan tahun lalu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu, kumohon
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,tolong rahasiakan keberadaannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini benar-benar kau, Sylvie?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memangnya kau makan berapa banyak Mana Core\Nsaat aku tak ada?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.95,0:16:37.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Sylvie!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.18,0:16:42.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umur 11 tahun menguasai empat elemen,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,punya dua atribut tambahan
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan menjadikan naga sebagai rekannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.18,0:16:51.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Levelnya sungguh berbeda jauh denganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Elijah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.90,0:16:59.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka kabur.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku bisa mengantar kalian ke kota\Ndengan lebih cepat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.98,0:17:35.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanti malah jadi tontonan\Nkalau ada naga lewat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.55,0:17:41.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau terlihat lebih keren tanpa topeng.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Samantha.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan banyak bicara dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Simpan tenagamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.96,0:17:50.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana Core Elder Wood?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.21,0:17:58.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak sengaja menemukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.45,0:18:03.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita bagi dengan yang lain\Nkalau situasinya sudah aman.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.18,0:18:06.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak butuh.\NKaulah yang pantas mendapatkannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.51,0:18:10.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga tak butuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.25,0:18:14.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tahu seberapa berharganya ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.95,0:18:18.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berkatmu, aku masih hidup sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.61,0:18:23.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kau yang berhak menerima hadiahnya.\NKupikir ini adil.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.18,0:18:32.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah. Terima kasih, semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.05,0:18:39.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dan Elijah akan pergi mencari\Nair minum.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.71,0:18:47.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus mengabari keluargaku\Nbahwa aku selamat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.25,0:18:59.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menangkap Mana Beast,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.45,0:19:05.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,lalu memakan Mana Core-nya\Nsampai jadi sebesar ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.78,0:19:08.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja aku menangkap banyak Mana Beast!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bisa kembali ke wujud aslimu?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.61,0:19:41.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dan Jasmine selamat.\NTak usah khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.61,0:19:42.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.35,0:19:47.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya akan baik-baik saja.\NDia pasti akan segera pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.31,0:20:05.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketua, ada tamu untuk Anda.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.15,0:20:10.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anda...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.51,0:20:38.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana keadaanmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah bisa pulang kapan pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.95,0:20:42.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.51,0:20:45.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, kami sudah merepotkanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.21,0:20:51.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan begitu. Kami pihak Guild sudah banyak\Nberutang budi pada party Twin Horn.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.41,0:20:54.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya saja...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.35,0:20:57.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penaklukan dungeon kali ini
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.38,0:21:00.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,dilakukan tanpa izin dari Guild.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.35,0:21:03.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ditambah dengan kondisi saat ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.98,0:21:07.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,ada laporan yang menuntut\Npertanggungjawaban kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.65,0:21:11.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Note, terkait hukumanmu,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.41,0:21:14.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan diputuskan oleh komite Guild.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pelapornya adalah Lucas Wykes.
